          <p class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-1">Assessment & Sleep History</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">We start by understanding your sleep: not just what's happening at night, but everything around it: your history, your patterns, your worries about sleep, and what you've already tried. This is not a quiz. It is a real conversation.</p>
